 George VI, and after his death in  1952  achieved great public affection as Queen Mother for nearly half a century. Even more influentially, it is the name of her daughter  Queen Elizabeth II  (  b. 1926 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elisabeth N was born in 1225. She married Marquard Langenmantel before 1235. They were the parents of at least 5 sons and 1 daughter."},"et":{"1225–":"1225–Surnud","1210–1288":"1210–1288","1235–Male":"1235–Surnud","1238–1293":"1238–1293","1239–Male":"1239–Surnud","1240–1301":"1240–1301","1252–1295":"1252–1295","1255–Female":"1255–Surnud","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1252":"1252","vor 1235":"enne 1235","1240":"1240","1295":"1295","1293":"1293","1239":"1239","1238":"1238","1225":"1225","       1239":"1239","1235":"1235","1301":"1301","1255":"1255","1288":"1288","1210":"1210","um 1238":"umbes 1238","about 1252":"umbes 1252","Augsburg, Augsburg, Bayern, Deutschland":"Augsburg, Augsburg, Bayern, Saksamaa","Augsburg, Augsburg, Bavaria, Germany":"Augsburg, Augsburg, Bayern, Saksamaa","Deutschland":"Saksamaa","Augsburg  Bayern, Deutschland":"Landkreis Augsburg, Bayern, Saksamaa","Augsburg, Bavaria, Germany":"Landkreis Augsburg, Bayern, Saksamaa","Augsburg,,Bayern,Deutschland":"Landkreis Augsburg, Bayern, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"1225–":"1225–Kuollut","1210–1288":"1210–1288","1235–Male":"1235–Kuollut","1238–1293":"1238–1293","1239–Male":"1239–Kuollut","1240–1301":"1240–1301","1252–1295":"1252–1295","1255–Female":"1255–Kuollut","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1252":"1252","vor 1235":"ennen vuotta 1235","1240":"1240","1295":"1295","1293":"1293","1239":"1239","1238":"1238","1225":"1225","       1239":"1239","1235":"1235","1301":"1301","1255":"1255","1288":"1288","1210":"1210","um 1238":"noin 1238","about 1252":"noin 1252","Augsburg, Augsburg, Bayern, Deutschland":"Augsburg, Augsburg, Bayern, Saksa","Augsburg, Augsburg, Bavaria, Germany":"Augsburg, Augsburg, Bayern, Saksa","Deutschland":"Saksa","Augsburg  Bayern, Deutschland":"Landkreis Augsburg, Bayern, Saksa","